Class BasicXListUI.ListDataHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jdesktop.swingx.plaf.basic.core.BasicXListUI.ListDataHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EventListener, ListDataListener
    Enclosing class:
    BasicXListUI

    public class BasicXListUI.ListDataHandler
extends Object
implements ListDataListener
    The ListDataListener that's added to the JLists model at installUI time, and whenever the JList.model property changes.

    Warning: Serialized objects of this class will not be compatible with future Swing releases. The current serialization support is appropriate for short term storage or RMI between applications running the same version of Swing. As of 1.4, support for long term storage of all JavaBeansTM has been added to the java.beans package. Please see XMLEncoder.

    See Also:
    JList.getModel(), BasicXListUI.maybeUpdateLayoutState(), BasicXListUI.createListDataListener(), BasicXListUI.installUI(javax.swing.JComponent)
